My exams went allright. Might have been better if I studied.

::EndBringer/Demise/Greven::

EndBringer frowns at the question, realizing he had no actual idea 
where Killfest was at the moment. He sends a short query through the 
communication system available to only Killfest and his team, and 
soon gets Killfest's location.

EndBringer reports the coordinates to Astrotrain (I'm too lazy to 
make up some fancy grid name and number, so we'll leave it at 'the 
coordinates'), and sits down on the floor, waiting to be off.



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "rAuq" <rauq@t...> wrote:
> After EndBringer, Demise, and Grenven are inside Astrotrain asks 
> EndBringer, "What are the coordinates to your the location of your 
> commander?" The intercom static snaps, underlining Astrotrain's 
> impatience...
